org.wiredwidgets.cow.webapp.client.bpm

Class Template

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.wiredwidgets.cow.webapp.client.bpm.Template

  • public class Template
extends Object
    Stores a tree of Activity objects for a saved workflow. Workflows always start with an Activities, but the Template uses a special type of Activities called BaseList. This is not required by the XML schema, but it is enforced in the GUI.
    Author:
    JSTASIK
